import React from 'react';

function iPhone() {
    return (
    <svg

      version="1"
      viewBox="0 0 64 64"
      xmlSpace="preserve"
      width="3rem" 
      height="3rem"

      <g fill="white">
        <path d="M48 0H16c-2.211 0-4 1.789-4 4v56c0 2.211 1.789 4 4 4h32c2.211 0 4-1.789 4-4V4c0-2.211-1.789-4-4-4zm2 60a2 2 0 01-2 2H16a2 2 0 01-2-2v-8h36v8zm0-10H14V10h36v40zm0-42H14V4a2 2 0 012-2h32a2 2 0 012 2v4z"></path>

        <circle cx="37" cy="5" r="1"></circle>
      </g>
    </svg>    
    )
}

export default iPhone;
